@startuml
title <font size=12>Laporan Laba Rugi Owner</font>

actor Owner
participant "Browser"
participant "Controller"
participant "Database"
participant "View"

Owner -> Browser: Akses Laporan Laba Rugi\n(filter tanggal awal & akhir)
Browser -> Controller: GET /pemilik/laporan-laba-rugi\n(tanggal_awal, tanggal_akhir)

Controller -> Database: Query Transaksi\n(dengan filter tanggal)
Database --> Controller: Return semua transaksi\nyang sesuai

Controller -> Controller: Loop setiap transaksi\n& detail transaksi

Controller -> Controller: Hitung per item:\n- Harga jual\n- Harga beli\n- Laba = Jual - Beli

Controller -> Controller: Aggregate per tanggal:\n- Total Pendapatan\n- Total Modal\n- Total Laba

Controller -> Controller: Hitung total keseluruhan:\n- Total Pendapatan\n- Total Modal\n- Total Laba\n- Margin Keuntungan (%)

Controller -> View: Pass data laporan harian\n& ringkasan total

View --> Browser: Display laporan dengan:\n- Tabel detail per hari\n- Grafik Pendapatan vs Modal\n- Summary box Laba/Rugi

Browser --> Owner: Tampilkan hasil laporan
@enduml
